Introduction
------------

I wrote this program to help people out of common problems - I hope it helps!

It works in the same way as Teletext - You type in the page number using the
keyboard, Troubleshooter finds it and displays it on the screen.

Using the '+' and '-' keys on the keyboard, you can advance or backtrack one
page.


